{"tid":1535784,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"無差別攻入學校 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-09-03T13:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:18:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"775a8463400de8d2acf75fdb0b3d2acc8d267df0","tid":1535784,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190903/20760731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F20760731&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=3360a9f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F20760731&h=b5db7c72\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20190903/20760731</a><br />\n<br />\n無差別攻入學校 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190903/large/1567408022_1c4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190903%2Flarge%2F1567408022_1c4b.jpg&h=71b49284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林奠領導香港黑府，做晒慈母戲，哽咽關心克警子女遭欺凌，其他人的子女，在她眼中，no stake啊還用說！在太子港鐵站重演721元朗一幕，速龍衝入車廂兇狠揮棍噴椒，指控市民是「喬裝市民」（？）係咁打的畫面，與鄉黑融合了！回到學校，辦學團體通常親建制，避談政治。但政治已經變成克警抓狂、每隔柒秒放一炮的催淚彈，山埃會無差別攻入，話之你是食肆抑或老人院。學校，隨時出狀況。一，愛字頭召集圍校，騷擾兼起底罷課的師生，當校長室係區議員辦公室和大埔連儂牆，噁心潑糞，點搞？二，知法犯法的克警卧底，不單扮抗爭者擲汽油彈，還會混入校園「喬裝」插班生進行大抓捕。鄧二哥命令校長配合，這個角色冇包括跪求別開槍，點演？三，689公然吹雞，體制以外的力量收到，向校區推進。白衫藍衫聯乘黑警，扯開校門鐵閘，用木棍教仔，這一課，算做乜科？班主任，點教？四，灰色恐怖，瀰漫校園。呢隻灰，叫做篤灰。比水炮車更藍的校長篤老師，跟學生齊上齊落的教師絕望了，化為灰燼了。校園變成良知的墓園，家長們，點頂？ <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n驚慄片 (尊子)"},{"pid":"ca0393ff909d7301bbf82f3c672872f28c9db512","tid":1535784,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:18:01.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"c1da798d151ec3b2203b2a859b4cfd1a8b49b4e1","tid":1535784,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}